<p align="center" class="loinoidau">L&#7900;I N&Oacute;I &#272;&#7846;U</p>
<p align="center" class="loinoidau">&nbsp;</p>
<p>L&agrave; nh&#7919;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i con c&#7911;a &#273;&#7845;t Th&#7915;a Thi&ecirc;n-Hu&#7871;, &#273;&#432;&#7907;c th&#7915;a h&#432;&#7903;ng truy&#7873;n th&#7889;ng c&#7911;a qu&ecirc; h&#432;&#417;ng, c&#7911;a cha &ocirc;ng, gia &#273;&igrave;nh, ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i lu&ocirc;n lu&ocirc;n tr&#259;n tr&#7903; &#273;&#7875; l&agrave;m sao g&oacute;p ph&#7847;n nh&#7887; v&agrave;o ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n tinh th&#7847;n Hi&#7871;u H&#7885;c t&#7915; ng&agrave;n x&#432;a cho c&aacute;c th&#7871; h&#7879; mai sau nh&#7845;t l&agrave; nh&#7919;ng em &#7903; v&ugrave;ng s&acirc;u, v&ugrave;ng xa, mi&#7873;n qu&ecirc; c&ograve;n nhi&#7873;u kh&oacute; kh&#259;n trong cu&#7897;c s&#7889;ng v&agrave; h&#7885;c t&#7853;p c&oacute; c&#417; h&#7897;i &#273;&#7871;n tr&#432;&#7901;ng v&agrave; tr&#7903; th&agrave;nh nh&#7919;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i c&oacute; &iacute;ch cho gia &#273;&igrave;nh, x&oacute;m l&agrave;ng v&agrave; x&atilde; h&#7897;i. Ch&#7881; c&oacute; c&aacute;i h&#7885;c m&#7899;i gi&uacute;p ch&uacute;ng ta tho&aacute;t kh&#7887;i &#273;&oacute;i ngh&egrave;o v&agrave; ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n theo t&#7847;m v&oacute;c c&#7911;a c&aacute;c n&#432;&#7899;c ti&ecirc;n ti&#7871;n tr&ecirc;n th&#7871; gi&#7899;i.</p>
<p>V&#7899;i tinh th&#7847;n &ldquo;L&aacute; l&agrave;nh &#273;&ugrave;m l&aacute; r&aacute;ch&rdquo;, &ldquo;Ng&#432;&#7901;i &#273;i tr&#432;&#7899;c r&#432;&#7899;c ng&#432;&#7901;i &#273;i sau&rdquo;, &ldquo;U&#7889;ng n&#432;&#7899;c nh&#7899; ngu&#7891;n&rdquo;, &ldquo;M&#7897;t c&acirc;y l&agrave;m ch&#7859;ng n&ecirc;n non, ba c&acirc;y ch&#7909;m l&#7841;i n&ecirc;n th&agrave;nh n&uacute;i cao&rdquo;&hellip; ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i k&ecirc;u g&#7885;i s&#7921; &#273;&oacute;ng g&oacute;p c&#7911;a t&#7845;t c&#7843; con d&acirc;n c&#7911;a qu&ecirc; h&#432;&#417;ng v&agrave; th&acirc;n h&#7919;u t&#7915; trong n&#432;&#7899;c ra &#273;&#7871;n h&#7843;i ngo&#7841;i &#273;&#7875; gi&uacute;p v&agrave;o vi&#7879;c huy &#273;&#7897;ng c&ocirc;ng s&#7913;c, tr&iacute; tu&#7879; v&agrave; v&#7853;t l&#7921;c &#273;&#7875; gi&uacute;p &#273;&#7905; nh&#7919;ng em h&#7885;c sinh &#7903; qu&ecirc; ngh&egrave;o, ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i nh&#7919;ng th&agrave;nh vi&ecirc;n &#273;&#7891;ng s&aacute;ng l&#7853;p l&agrave; nh&#7919;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i t&igrave;nh nguy&#7879;n g&oacute;p nh&#7919;ng vi&ecirc;n g&#7841;ch &#273;&#7847;u ti&ecirc;n &#273;&#7875; x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng n&#7873;n m&oacute;ng cho &ldquo;Ch&#432;&#417;ng Tr&igrave;nh H&#7885;c B&#7893;ng Hu&#7871; Hi&#7871;u H&#7885;c&rdquo; , l&agrave; ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh kh&#7903;i &#273;&#7897;ng &#273;&#7875; th&#259;m d&ograve;, r&uacute;t kinh nghi&#7879;m d&agrave;nh cho c&aacute;c h&#7885;c sinh c&#7845;p 2 ngh&egrave;o v&agrave; v&#432;&#7907;t kh&oacute; v&#7899;i k&#7923; v&#7885;ng s&#7869; c&oacute; nh&#7919;ng ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh k&#7871; ti&#7871;p l&#7899;n h&#417;n, m&#7841;nh h&#417;n v&agrave; c&oacute; thi&#7871;t th&#7921;c h&#417;n n&#7919;a trong vi&#7879;c vun &#273;&#7855;p, ph&aacute;t huy truy&#7873;n th&#7889;ng Hi&#7871;u H&#7885;c c&#7911;a qu&ecirc; h&#432;&#417;ng, c&#7911;a d&acirc;n t&#7897;c Vi&#7879;t.</p><p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong>1.&nbsp;M&#7908;C TI&Ecirc;U :</strong></p>
<p><strong>1.1.</strong> &#272;o&agrave;n  k&#7871;t r&#7897;ng r&atilde;i , kh&ocirc;ng ph&acirc;n bi&#7879;t ngu&#7891;n g&#7889;c, th&agrave;nh ph&#7847;n, d&acirc;n t&#7897;c, t&ocirc;n gi&aacute;o, gi&agrave;u ngh&egrave;o&hellip; c&#7911;a t&#7845;t c&#7843; nh&#7919;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i c&oacute; t&#7845;m l&ograve;ng v&#7899;i qu&ecirc; h&#432;&#417;ng &#273;&#7875; t&#7841;o n&ecirc;n s&#7913;c m&#7841;nh Ph&ugrave; &#272;&#7893;ng trong t&#432;&#417;ng th&acirc;n t&#432;&#417;ng tr&#7907;, gi&uacute;p nhau v&#432;&#7907;t kh&oacute; v&agrave; ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n.</p>
<p><strong>1.2.</strong> Gi&uacute;p cho c&aacute;c em h&#7885;c sinh ngh&egrave;o ph&#7847;n n&agrave;o c&#417;m &#259;n ,&aacute;o m&#7863;c, h&#7885;c c&#7909;&hellip; &#273;&#7875; t&#7899;i tr&#432;&#7901;ng, v&#7873; l&acirc;u d&agrave;i (th&ecirc;m s&#7919;a, d&#7909;ng c&#7909; th&#7875; thao&hellip;) c&#7843;i thi&#7879;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c s&#7913;c kho&#7867; c&#7911;a c&aacute;c em k&eacute;m may m&#7855;n.</p>
<p><strong>1.3.</strong> Do b&#432;&#7899;c &#273;&#7847;u n&ecirc;n t&#7853;p trung v&agrave;o c&aacute;c em h&#7885;c c&#7845;p 2 (l&#7899;p 6-9), l&agrave; nh&#7919;ng em ph&#7843;i &#273;&#432;&#7907;c b&#7843;o v&#7879;, tr&aacute;nh lao &#273;&#7897;ng v&#7845;t v&#7843; &#7843;nh h&#432;&#7903;ng &#273;&#7871;n vi&#7879;c ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n tinh th&#7847;n v&agrave; th&#7875; l&#7921;c c. L&#7913;a tu&#7893;i c&#7845;p 2 c&oacute; nh&#7853;n th&#7913;c t&#432;&#417;ng &#273;&#7889;i t&#7889;t v&#7873; &#273;&#7897;ng c&#417; h&#7885;c t&#7853;p v&agrave; &yacute; th&#7913;c ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n.</p>
<p><strong>1.4.</strong>T&#7915;ng b&#432;&#7899;c bi&#7871;n ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh th&agrave;nh ho&agrave;n ch&#7881;nh v&agrave; ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n th&ecirc;m nhi&#7873;u ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh gi&uacute;p c&aacute;c em c&#7845;p1, c&#7845;p 3, h&#7885;c ngh&#7873;, cao &#273;&#7859;ng, &#273;&#7841;i h&#7885;c&hellip;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong>2.&nbsp;C&Aacute;C Y&Ecirc;U C&#7846;U :</strong></p><p><strong>2.1. &#272;&#7889;i t&#432;&#7907;ng nh&#7853;n t&agrave;i tr&#7907;:</strong></p>
<p>&#8226; H&#7885;c sinh ngh&egrave;o &#7903; v&ugrave;ng qu&ecirc;, h&#7885;c kh&aacute; gi&#7887;i, c&oacute; ch&iacute; hi&#7871;u h&#7885;c, t&#432;&#417;ng th&acirc;n t&#432;&#417;ng tr&#7907;, hi&#7871;u th&#7843;o, c&oacute; t&igrave;nh l&agrave;ng ngh&#297;a x&oacute;m(gia &#273;&igrave;nh neo &#273;&#417;n, &#273;au &#7889;m t&agrave;n t&#7853;t, m&#7891; c&ocirc;i s&#7869; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#432;u ti&ecirc;n).</p>
<p>&#8226; C&aacute;c em ngh&egrave;o nh&#432;ng h&#7885;c c&ograve;n y&#7871;u c&#361;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c h&#7893; tr&#7907; n&#7871;u c&oacute; h&#432;&#7899;ng ti&#7871;n b&#7897; v&agrave; kinh ph&iacute; cho ph&eacute;p .</p>
<p><strong>2.2. &#272;&#7883;nh m&#7913;c t&agrave;i tr&#7907;:</strong> &#272;&#7875; t&#7853;p trung v&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng t&#7841;o s&#7921; ph&acirc;n bi&#7879;t n&ecirc;n ch&#7881; c&oacute; m&#7897;t lo&#7841;i t&agrave;i tr&#7907;:</p>
<p>- H&#7885;c b&#7893;ng Hu&#7871; Hi&#7871;u H&#7885;c : bao g&#7891;m ti&#7873;n 500.000&#273;/n&#259;m d&agrave;nh cho c&aacute;c em h&#7885;c sinh ngh&egrave;o v&#432;&#7907;t kh&oacute; trong h&#7885;c t&#7853;p v&agrave; cu&#7897;c s&#7889;ng..</p>
<p><strong>2.3. </strong></p>
<p><strong>a- </strong>Ngu&#7891;n t&agrave;i ch&iacute;nh c&#7845;p h&#7885;c b&#7893;ng s&#7869; do c&aacute;c nh&agrave; h&#7843;o t&acirc;m, c&aacute;c gia &#273;&igrave;nh, c&aacute;c doanh nghi&#7879;p&hellip;t&agrave;i tr&#7907;, &#273;&oacute;ng g&oacute;p theo tinh th&#7847;n t&#7921; nguy&#7879;n, &#273;&oacute;ng g&oacute;p v&agrave;o b&#7845;t c&#7913; l&uacute;c n&agrave;o thu&#7853;n ti&#7879;n cho nh&agrave; t&agrave;i tr&#7907;.</p>
<p>M&#7913;c &#273;&oacute;ng g&oacute;p c&oacute; th&#7875; t&#7915; v&agrave;i &#273;&ocirc; ho&#7863;c v&agrave;i ch&#7909;c ng&agrave;n &#273;&#7891;ng tr&#7903; l&ecirc;n. Nhi&#7873;u &#273;&oacute;ng g&oacute;p nh&#7887; s&#7869; t&#7841;o ra nh&#7919;ng h&#7885;c b&#7893;ng qu&yacute; gi&aacute; cho c&aacute;c em h&#7885;c sinh ngh&egrave;o hi&#7871;u h&#7885;c.</p>
<p>Ngo&agrave;i ra c&aacute;c &#273;&oacute;ng g&oacute;p cho Tr&#432;&#7901;ng, &#273;&#7883;a ph&#432;&#417;ng k&egrave;m theo danh x&#432;ng v&agrave; mang t&ecirc;n m&#7897;t c&aacute; nh&acirc;n theo y&ecirc;u c&#7847;u c&#7911;a nh&agrave; t&agrave;i tr&#7907; c&#361;ng s&#7869; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n. T&ecirc;n v&agrave; danh x&#432;ng ph&#7843;i tu&acirc;n theo ph&aacute;t lu&#7853;t VN v&agrave; theo ti&ecirc;u chi v&agrave; m&#7909;c &#273;&iacute;ch c&#7911;a &quot;Qu&#7929; H&#7885;c B&#7893;ng Hu&#7871; Hi&#7871;u H&#7885;c&quot;.</p>
<p> <strong>b- </strong>&#272;&#7897;ng vi&ecirc;n, s&#7917; d&#7909;ng c&ocirc;ng s&#7913;c, tr&iacute; tu&#7879; c&#7911;a t&#7845;t c&#7843; m&#7885;i ng&#432;&#7901;i &#7911;ng h&#7897; Ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh Hu&#7871; Hi&#7871;u H&#7885;c.</p>
<p> <strong>c- </strong>Nh&#7919;ng &#273;&oacute;ng g&oacute;p b&#7857;ng v&#7853;t ph&#7849;m: v&#7843;i, &aacute;o qu&#7847;n m&#7899;i, &aacute;o qu&#7847;n c&#361;, c&#7863;p v&#7903;, s&aacute;ch, vi&#7871;t, d&#7909;ng c&#7909; h&#7885;c t&#7853;p (m&aacute;y vi t&iacute;nh.v.v...), g&#7841;o....</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong>3. TH&#7900;I GIAN:</strong> </p><p>D&#7921; ki&#7871;n b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u v&agrave;o n&#259;m h&#7885;c 2005-2006, kho&#7843;ng th&#7901;i gian Hu&#7871; t&#7893; ch&#7913;c Festiva s&#7869; ph&aacute;t cho c&aacute;c em t&#7841;i tr&#432;&#7901;ng theo h&#7885;c hay m&#7897;t &#273;&#7883;a &#273;i&#7875;m t&#7853;p trung (m&#7895;i h&#7885;c b&#7893;ng s&#7869; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ph&aacute;t 1 l&#7847;n /n&#259;m) v&agrave; c&aacute;c n&#259;m sau s&#7869; ph&aacute;t s&#7899;m h&#417;n n&#7871;u ch&#7911; &#273;&#7897;ng ngu&#7891;n t&agrave;i tr&#7907;. </p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong>4.&nbsp;PH&#431;&#416;NG TH&#7912;C HO&#7840;T &#272;&#7896;NG:</strong></p>
<p><strong>4.1. T&ocirc;n ch&#7881; v&agrave; t&#7893; ch&#7913;c:</strong> L&agrave; ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh x&atilde; h&#7897;i, kh&ocirc;ng v&#7909; l&#7907;i, m&#7895;i ng&#432;&#7901;i v&igrave; m&#7885;i ng&#432;&#7901;i, s&#7869; c&oacute;:</p>
<p>- H&#7897;i &#273;&#7891;ng c&#7889; v&#7845;n</p>
<p>- H&#7897;i &#273;&#7891;ng s&aacute;ng l&#7853;p</p>
<p>- Ban b&#7843;o tr&#7907;</p>
<p>- Ban &#273;i&#7873;u h&agrave;nh</p>
<p>- C&aacute;c th&agrave;nh vi&ecirc;n , c&aacute;c c&#7897;ng t&aacute;c vi&ecirc;n ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng t&#7921; nguy&#7879;n kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; l&#432;&#417;ng.</p>
<p>(Sau khi ho&agrave;n ch&#7881;nh &#273;&#7873; &aacute;n, H&#7897;i &#273;&#7891;ng c&#7889; v&#7845;n, H&#7897;i &#273;&#7891;ng s&aacute;ng l&#7853;p s&#7869; h&#7885;p (d&#7921; ki&#7871;n th&aacute;ng 12-2005) &#273;&#7875; th&ocirc;ng qua giao &#432;&#7899;c c&#7911;a ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh v&agrave; &#273;&#7873; c&#7917; m&#7897;t Ban &#273;i&#7873;u h&agrave;nh).</p>
<p><strong>4.2. Th&#7875; th&#7913;c xin c&#7845;p h&#7885;c b&#7893;ng:</strong></p><p>- H&#7885;c sinh t&#7921; vi&#7871;t &#273;&#417;n xin tr&igrave;nh b&agrave;y ho&agrave;n c&#7843;nh, h&#7885;c l&#7921;c v&agrave; &#432;&#7899;c mong k&egrave;m theo c&aacute;c gi&#7845;y t&#7901; kh&aacute;c n&#7871;u c&oacute; ( th&#432; gi&#7899;i thi&#7879;u c&#7911;a Th&#7847;y C&ocirc;, th&agrave;nh t&iacute;ch h&#7885;c t&#7853;p...)</p>
<p>- Th&#7901;i gian n&#7897;p v&agrave;o &#273;&#7847;u h&#7885;c k&#7923; : h&#7841;n ch&oacute;t nh&#7853;n &#273;&#417;n v&agrave;o gi&#7919;a th&aacute;ng 11 cho n&#259;m 2005 v&agrave; cu&#7889;i th&aacute;ng 9 cho c&aacute;c n&#259;m sau.</p>
<p>- S&#7889; &#273;&#417;n xin c&#7845;p c&#7847;n g&#7845;p &#273;&ocirc;i s&#7889; h&#7885;c b&#7893;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c c&#7845;p &#273;&#7875; vi&#7879;c x&eacute;t duy&#7879;t c&oacute; gi&aacute; tr&#7883; h&#417;n.</p>
<p>- H&#7885;c b&#7893;ng c&oacute; th&#7875; b&#7883; c&#7855;t n&#7871;u c&aacute;c em vi ph&#7841;m &#273;&#7841;o &#273;&#7913;c, k&#7927; lu&#7853;t, h&#7885;c h&agrave;nh sa s&uacute;t...</p>
<p>- H&#7885;c b&#7893;ng c&oacute; th&#7875; b&#7883; c&#7855;t n&#7871;u c&oacute; &#273;&#417;n khi&#7871;u n&#7841;i ho&#7863;c t&#7889; c&aacute;o ng&#432;&#7901;i nh&#7853;n kh&ocirc;ng trung th&#7921;c trong xin c&#7845;p h&#7885;c b&#7893;ng.</p>
<p><strong>4.3. H&#7897;i &#273;&#7891;ng x&eacute;t duy&#7879;t:</strong> G&#7891;m c&aacute;c th&agrave;nh vi&ecirc;n trong h&#7897;i &#273;&#7891;ng c&#7889; v&#7845;n, h&#7897;i &#273;&#7891;ng s&aacute;ng l&#7853;p, ban b&#7843;o tr&#7907;, ban &#273;i&#7873;u h&agrave;nh,Ban &#272;i&#7873;u H&agrave;nh , s&#7869; ph&#7889;i h&#7907;p v&#7899;i S&#7903; Gi&aacute;o D&#7909;c v&agrave; &#272;&agrave;o T&#7841;o;c&aacute;c Ph&ograve;ng Gi&aacute;o D&#7909;c ,B&aacute;o Th&#7915;a Thi&ecirc;n Hu&#7871;;B&aacute;o Tu&#7893;i Tr&#7867; &#273;&#7875; c&ocirc;ng khai th&ocirc;ng tin .C&aacute;c c&#7897;ng t&aacute;c vi&ecirc;n &#7903; Th&#7915;a Thi&ecirc;n Hu&#7871; r&#7845;t c&#7847;n &#273;&#7871;n &#273;&ecirc;&rsquo; c&oacute; x&aacute;c minh t&#7841;i nh&agrave; nh&#7857;m trao h&#7885;c b&#7893;ng &#273;&#7871;n nh&#7919;ng em x&#7913;ng &#273;&aacute;ng nh&#7845;t.</p>
<p>&#272;&aacute;nh gi&aacute; theo thang 100 &#273;i&#7875;m:</p>
<p>&#8226; Ho&agrave;n c&#7843;nh kh&oacute; kh&#259;n : 40 &#273;i&#7875;m</p>
<p>&#8226;  Tinh th&#7847;n hi&#7871;u h&#7885;c v&#432;&#7907;t kh&oacute; : 40 &#273;i&#7875;m</p>
